This is the last version of LocalShops - There will be no more updates unless another developer picks up support for it.

Version 4.1.0

* Fixed /shop info - was displaying buy/sell information backwards
* Fixed logic in SignUpdater being written completely wrong
* Added a break check for shop creation to prevent players from creating shops in areas they can't break blocks.
* Updated for latest Vault & Bukkit
* Fixed shop set message returning a %% with the ITEMNAME
* Added ability to delete shops by Id